  "text": "Spectroscopic experiments were performed by using a commercial steady-state absorption spectrometer (V 670, Jasco), a home-built femtosecond transient-absorption spectrometer setup and a 2D setup in fully noncollinear box geometry optimized for pulses in the ultraviolet regime [CITATION_1] .",
